政上的主要障礙有那些？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "19a86c3bcad5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112090", "c": "304", "s": "0309", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "地方政府與政治", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-00076', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-112-c4ffbd92', 'sub-heelevel3-c5fb3965-04', NULL, 'essay', '依照司法院釋字第498號解釋，我國「地方行政機關與地方立法機關間依
法並有權責制衡關係」，與其他國家地方立法與行政關係不盡相同，若以
美國地方的議會／市經理制為例，請從行政與立法權責關係比較我國地
方自治組織制度特徵與美國議會／市經理制的差異。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "19a86c3bcad5", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112090", "c": "304", "s": "0309", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "地方政府與政治", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "戶政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-00077', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965', 'heelevel3-c5fb3965-moex-112-c4ffbd92', 'sub-heelevel3-c5fb3965-04', NULL, 'essay', '依相關法制規定，中央政府對地方政府應如何貫徹自治監督？如果地方
